"   </a>",
"   <a class=\"icontxt textLink etacLink\" href=\"#\" title=\"Email graphic(s)\">",
"    Email",
"   </a>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Cutaneous sarcoidosis",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 293px; height: 432px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Flat-topped, round or polygonal papules are present on the neck. In addition, there are multiple 1 to 3 mm round, shiny, skin colored papules in groups at the base of the neck, resembling lichen nitidus.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
